&lt;h3 id="环境配置">环境配置
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>配置安装模块的路径，默认会安装到C盘下&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/oopooa/cdn/post/node5.webp"
loading="lazy"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>在安装目录下新建两个文件夹&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">node_cache
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">node_global
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>打开 &lt;code>cmd&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">npm config set prefix &amp;#34;E:\Node\node_global&amp;#34;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">npm config set cache &amp;#34;E:\Node\node_cache&amp;#34;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/oopooa/cdn/post/node6.webp"
loading="lazy"
>&lt;/p>
