&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/oopooa/cdn/post/node11.webp"
loading="lazy"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="hexo">Hexo
&lt;/h2>&lt;h3 id="安装-1">安装
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>打开cmd&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">npm install -g hexo-cli
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>进入事先准备好的博客文件根目录&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/oopooa/cdn/post/hexo.webp"
loading="lazy"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>右键 &amp;ndash;&amp;gt; Git Bash Here&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">npm i
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>这个命令会跟据你的 package.json 依赖来新增或删除一些模块，一般不会有太大的变化。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>最后 &lt;code>Hexo&lt;/code> 三连&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">hexo clean &amp;amp;&amp;amp; hexo g &amp;amp;&amp;amp; hexo s
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="测试-2">测试
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>浏览器访问: http://localhost:4000/&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/oopooa/cdn/post/hexo2.webp"
loading="lazy"
>&lt;/p>
